Copy usertype.dat to \Microsoft Visual Studio 10.0\Common7\IDE\usertype.dat

For Visual Studio 2010:
Copy autoexp.dat to \Microsoft Visual Studio 10\Common7\Packages\Debugger\autoexp.dat file.

For Visual Studio 2012:
Copy coid.natvis into \Microsoft Visual Studio 11\Common7\Packages\Debugger\Visualizers\ directory.

For Visual Studio 2013:
Copy coid.natvis into \Microsoft Visual Studio 12\Common7\Packages\Debugger\Visualizers\ directory.

For Visual Studio 2015:
Copy coid.natvis into \Microsoft Visual Studio 14\Common7\Packages\Debugger\Visualizers\ directory.